name: Biting, Crunchy, B.wav
description: More raw audio of biting into crunchy and crispy prawn crackers. The chewing has been edited out, the sounds are simply each initial (and loud) bite of the cracker. I couldn't resist ordering another Chinese takeaway. The last three crunches are continuous without any editing break in between. This sound is not in the public domain. 1.	a quick, involuntary inhalation that follows a spasm of the diaphragm and is suddenly checked by closure of the glottis, producing a short, relatively sharp sound.

name: My Hungry Stomach's Hungriest Sounds
description: My first sound recording for my new sound album. My stomach is feeling all grumbly! It continuously seems like it hungrily and sometimes angrily rumbles like a monster, because it is very empty, and I had no food for over 50 hours. And I had to wait a little while longer to eat something.

name: My Starving Stomach Moans
description: Now I spent 230 hours without food, and I was resting, caressing my stomach this whole time, and I forgot to mention I was in my same clothes: my bathing bikini suit with my high-heeled multistrapped sandals; this entire time. My stomach can't wait any longer. It needs to be fed now! Ooooooooooooouuuuugh!!!

name: The Deepest & Heaviest Grumbly Hunger Growls & Moans of My Empty Stomach
description: Oooooooooouuuuuuuuuugggh! My stomach...so...hungry...! Need...food...! So...starving! My stomach is even hungrier than before, and I tried to calm my stomach down, but it wouldn't stop making those monstrous moans. Oooooooooohhhh!!!

name: Low Stomach Moans, Roars, & Grumbles and Hunger Growls & Gurgles of My Empty Stomach
description: Now I waited 220 hours without food. And my stomach is getting even angrier than ever before! Ooooooh! I'm so hungry!!!

name: My Hungry, Grumbling Stomach's Long, Deepest, and Lowest-Pitched Hunger Growl
description: My stomach is getting more hungrier just after 35 hours now. Ooough!

name: The Famished Bubbling Roars of My Grumbling Stomach
description: Oooooooouggh!! My stomach is now getting more hungrier than ever, and even angrier. It has been 82 hours without food. I need to eat something, but now just now.

name: My Stomach's Low Hunger Growls
description: Oooooooooooooooouuuugh! Uuuuuugggggh! My stomach is somehow measuring time on how long I waited to eat, and it has been 244 hours without any food or meals! It won't leave me alone because it is very hungry, and not only it was angrily and hungrily growling, but it was also telling me, "Grrrrr!!! Feed me! Feeeeeeed me!!! Brrrrrrrrrrgloooooooooooooooormmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm!!!!!!!" And I decided to wait some more.

name: Intensive Hunger Moans & Deep-Pitched Grumbles of My Stomach
description: Ooooooouuuuugh!!! My stomach is now becoming monstrous, and more intensive because I was now waiting for 225 hours to eat, and I'm feeling even more hungrier than I already am!

name: My Stomach Grumbles
description: I'm really hungry! Oooooh! Another boring 58 hours! Oh, dear!!!

name: My Tummy's Intensive Moans & Hunger Rumbles
description: My stomach waited for 126 hours now. Now it is acting like a wild monstrous beast in a cave. Oooooooooooooooooooooooough! I don't feel like myself anymore! So hungry...! Ugggggh! Ooooooooooouuuuuugh! Ohhhhh!

name: Hungry As a Bear
description: I'm so starving! Ooooooooooooooooooouuuuuuugh! My stomach! It's rumbling like a bear! It's been 120 hours now. It's getting intenser and intenser!

name: My Stomach's Angriest Message of Hunger
description: Now my belly is trying to angrily tell me that we have been waiting for hours for food, this means about 212 hours without any food. Oh, dear! What do I do now?

name: HungryStomach.wav
description:
Recorded on a TASCAM ZOOM H4n with XY capsule set to 90°. Close perspective MONO recording.

Stomach growling, wanting food.

name: My Stomach's Biggest & Longest Hunger Sounds Ever
description: Oooooooouuuuuuuuggggghhh!!! 250 hours...and my belly is still waiting to be fed. I don't know what else to do, but to keep waiting since I love my own hunger growls all this time! It was making the biggest, the longest hunger sounds ever! It was trying to tell me something---something that involves it needs to be fed right now, but I decided to wait a little longer more.

name: gargling bathroom sink.wav
description:
The water drain from our bathroom sink produced a strange gargling sound, as if being strangled. Before cleaning the drain, I made these recordings.
Recordings made in the rather small bathroom with a Zoom H4 recorder about 3/4 of a meter from the drain. It was recorded in Lyngby, Copenhagen in August 2020.
The recordings include water running into the sink, and draining. This is repeated 3 times, the last time the sink is almost entirely filled . and completely drained.

description: Ooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooouuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuggggggggggggggggggggghhhhhhh!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Uggggggggggh! 260 whole hours without food, my grumbling stomach is very hungry and angry. Seriously, I need to eat something, but I decided to wait a while longer to eat.

name: Hungry As a Lion
description: My poor tummy won't stop grumbling! Oooooouuugh! I need food! My stomach really needs it now, and it has been 235 hours now. But I decided to wait a while longer. I don't know how long I'm going to take this starving moment, but my angry stomach is getting more hungrier as a lion!

name: My Tummy Seriously Wants Food Now!
description: I'm verrrrrrry hungry! Ooooooooooooooooooooouuuuuuuuugh!!!! 255 hours! Oh my gosh! Oh, dear! My stomach is very angrily growling continuously. Oh, my! It seriously wants food now! And still, I'm waiting...! I probably won't eat at this second...never!

name: Slurping Sound (Variations: 1.Only with mouth 2.With liquid)
description:
Suction, swallowing, slurping and sounds. Plain mouthing/vocal sounds moving into coffee slurping sounds. Playful, humorous, relaxing, over-the-top and believable variations in succession.   

Technical Specifications: Recorded with a Zoom H6 recorder using the attached stereo XY microphones. The sound was post-processed to make it more crisp and impactful (basic EQ, dB adjustment and trimming on Reaper DAW). Recorded indoors in a semi-soundproofed room on a rainy and overcast afternoon in Pretoria, South Africa.

name: Stomach gurgling
description:
Mid/side recording of my stomach after having a fizzy drink. I laid down and placed the Zoom H2n directly on my stomach. All kinds of stomach ejactulations can be heard in addition to my heartbeat.

Raw 24/96 MS recording; be sure to decode before use. Left channel is mid, right is side.
To do this manually you should separate the channels to two mono tracks, duplicate the side track and invert the duplicate. Pan the side tracks hard left and right, and mix with the mono mid channel.

Or use a plugin to do it for you :D
